# General typescript rules

- apply to all typescript files **/*.ts
- Use type over interface
- Use functions over class
- Use function expressions over declarations
- Use const
- Break down code into small building blocks and compose using functional programming 
- Use named exports over default export
- Document all functions
- Create vitest unit tests when working with typescript
- Make sure unit tests pass
- All functions should be covered by unit tests
- Use Effect library to compose functions using pipe
  
